OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBills crisis: 'I'm paying  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor basics on credit'      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Working people say they are using      
OL,6, credit cards to top up energy meters   
OL,7, due to the pressure of high bills.     
OL,9,FChidi Uwakwe, who works full-time in a 
OL,10,Fhospital, said he was forced into the  
OL,11,Fmove so he could afford to buy food and
OL,12,Fdescribed the prospect of winter as a  
OL,13,F"nightmare".                           
OL,15,FCharity Citizens Advice said it had    
OL,16,Falready provided record levels of      
OL,17,Fcrisis support this year.              
OL,19,FThe government said it was focused on  
OL,20,Fhelping those who are struggling.      
